narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely! You watch great films and the workload isn't too hard. The seminar room is very open and it's an easy environment to contribute in.

I would recommended this class. Its nice concentrating on one director. KVK knows a lot about Forman's life, which is really interesting. The work load isn't bad. It is consistent- a film response once a week and then a midterm and final paper. Take it!
